Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:15.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could just die right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:29.17,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2280,1225)}A Place Further Than the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.50,Ep_Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Follow Backs\NDon't Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.50,Likes/Comments,sign,0000,0000,0000,,2 Likes\N0 Comments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.50,Hashtags,sign,0000,0000,0000,,#IFollowEveryoneWhoFollowsMe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:56.11,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,High school students. Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:55.92,sign_2764_6_3rd_annual_middl,sign,0000,0000,0000,,3rd annual middle-high school polar science contest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.11,0:01:57.76,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously doubt we'll find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:01:59.74,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.08,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.08,0:02:01.93,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:03.76,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you serve it hot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.88,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma says it's only May, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:07.77,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's only May, it's still hot out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:09.59,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I want cold tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:10.64,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,And some sweets with it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.98,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I request something of the pudding variety!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:15.28,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this is a bit bizarre?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:16.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Bizarre?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,This, from the girl who \Ncame up with our {\i1}last{\i0} plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:23.04,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Don't you realize \Nhow embarrassed we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.66,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It was our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.89,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:31.59,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:32.58,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,High school girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:39.34,sign_3662_27__High_School_Gir,sign,0000,0000,0000,,"High School Girl Goes to Antarctica!"\NA high school aged celebrity will be going on a\N three month trip to Antarctica with the civilian expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:39.34,sign_3662_28_Likes__29,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Likes: 29
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.74,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Goes to Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.91,0:02:40.41,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,"The planned civilian Antarctic \Nexpedition team has announced plans
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:44.02,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,to send a female high school \Nstudent with its news crew"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.70,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,"The accompanying student will \Nbe celebrity Shiraishi Yuzuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.66,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be doing online streams \Nabout the trip to Antarctica
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:52.98,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,and conditions at Syowa Station."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:54.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Someone beat me to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.68,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:59.27,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,The expedition members didn't \Nmention a thing about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.43,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,They probably realized the \Ntrouble it would cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.28,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:04.84,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Reporter... journalist... where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.04,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Um... um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.54,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi Yuzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.54,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.10,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Her agency is... Call this place right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,And say what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.51,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Ask them if I go along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:16.42,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the daughter of an Antarctic expedition \Nmember and a girl in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.91,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.25,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Call her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:22.23,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm not cut out \Nfor that sort of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.51,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They're all strangers, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.97,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gradually starting to \Nunderstand how this girl works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.02,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.39,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.24,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:39.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Talk! You want to go \Nto Antarctica, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:39.84,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.37,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you push this on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.82,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.39,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:47.26,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:51.86,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kobuchizawa Shirase-san, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.62,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:58.09,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure to meet you. \NMy name is Shiraishi Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.14,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.27,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,...Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.69,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't that the name of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.83,Main,mar,0000,0000,0000,,She's on wiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.52,Main,mar,0000,0000,0000,,A child actress who started in \Ncommercials at the age of five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,38,000 followers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.95,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Made her singing debut with \N"The Follow Backs Don't Stop."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:27.95,sign_6335_72_Shiraishi_Yuzuki,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi Yuzuki's 1st Single\NThe Follow Backs Don't Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.06,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I could just die right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.20,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:32.10,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Take a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:36.73,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Uploading my image to SNS without\Npermission is a violation of likeness rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.09,0:04:38.54,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Then can I get an autograph and a hand print?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.64,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a sumo wrestler!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.46,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.92,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I wanted to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.80,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.00,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Would you go to Antarctica in my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.73,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:51.35,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.55,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.88,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you leak it? \NA message board? Twitter? Your timeline?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.61,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I didn't leak it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.86,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.36,sign_21817_323_Orange,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.36,sign_21817_324_Reserved_Today_A,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Reserved Today\NAntarctic Expedition Informal\NMeet-up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.36,sign_21817_325_Sexy_Delicious__,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy Delicious!\NMeat Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:03.09,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the meet-up \Nin Shinjuku before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.03,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I had been invited, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.61,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:08.12,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.99,Main,hana,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you mean, in your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.87,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Put simply, I don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:20.00,sign_7541_99_TV_Program_Outli,sign,0000,0000,0000,,TV Program Outline\N{\fs16}High School Girl Goes to Antarctica!\N\N{\fs12}Blue Sky TV
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:18.67,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm originally from Hokkaido, so I'm \Nsick of the cold, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:23.34,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I think any high school girl going would \Nfit the requirements of the project, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:26.51,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.06,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.49,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:38.85,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Told you, didn't I? I told you \Nthat my plan would work perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:42.98,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, you said? Ridiculous, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.74,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Was this... part of the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.74,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It worked, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:49.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I've done it, Antarctica! \NAt last, Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.91,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, penguins!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, auroras!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.62,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.59,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, she's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.42,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the only way out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:05.96,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.38,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing your sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.24,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.51,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:18.56,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:23.44,sign_9098_126_New_Dosanko_Prom,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Dosanko Promotions\NProducer, Manager\N{\fs18\b1}Shiraishi Tamiko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.44,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,I am Yuzuki's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.06,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Shiraishi Tamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.48,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.70,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,I am also her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.30,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:33.70,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.70,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to go. \NIt's your job, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.78,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I told these girls they could do it instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:43.29,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think it's \Nyour place to decide that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.84,sign_7541_99_TV_Program_Outli,sign,0000,0000,0000,,TV Program Outline\N{\fs16}High School Girl Goes to Antarctica!\N\N{\fs12}Blue Sky TV
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:43.96,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.80,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:51.63,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,She just has to report on Antarctica, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:52.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I think she can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.63,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful, see? \NJust like a famous actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:58.98,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,Can she perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.89,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:06.65,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm c-currently... in... \NAntarctica... the weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hello! Can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I can perform! I'll handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:15.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I'm in Antarctica! \NPeople of Japan, are you seeing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:16.37,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be attractive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.43,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't sugar-coat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Okay, in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.00,sign_10574_152_Helping_Hands_Cl,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Helping Hands Class 2-3 Tamaki Mari
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.31,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:25.50,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What are we even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.76,sign_10790_157_Yeah____I_want_t,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I want to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:33.76,sign_10790_158_Can_t_do_that_ei,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12}Aina: {\fs14}Can't do that either?\N\N{\fs12}Yuri-chan: {\fs14}How about next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.27,Flashback,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.98,Flashback,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:46.98,Flashback,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This might be coming \Nout of nowhere, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:49.94,Flashback,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:51.28,sign_11268_163_How_about_next_S,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12}Yuri-chan: {\fs14}How about next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.95,sign_10790_157_Yeah____I_want_t,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...\NI don't know just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.95,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.51,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,When you reach your second year, \Nyou'll get more real time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.45,Main,tami,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you just bear with it for one year?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:01.72,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:04.51,Main,man,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry. I'll make \Nsure you're in time for entrance exa—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.33,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to high \Nschool for entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.52,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought we'd found a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.60,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad Shirase can't \Ntalk in front of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.27,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,But, Hinata-chan, you also couldn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.60,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to rub it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:28.52,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,That scarred her more than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.03,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:32.95,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:34.70,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Have what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:39.33,sign_9098_126_New_Dosanko_Prom,sign,0000,0000,0000,,New Dosanko Promotions\NProducer, Manager\N{\fs18\b1}Shiraishi Tamiko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.33,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Convince her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:43.08,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Apparently the girl is refusing to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.12,Flashback,tami,0000,0000,0000,,If you can convince her to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.68,Flashback,tami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll recommend to the production \Ncompany that you go as her companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.74,Flashback,tami,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.01,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if we can get her to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.62,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:58.01,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,But Yuzuki-chan left, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she has a job in Tokyo on Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:03.39,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,so she'll be staying in \Na hotel until Saturday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.64,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Friday, Saturday... two days?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.53,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there's no time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:08.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.87,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,It's after ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Then tomorrow morning, \Nbefore we go to school. Five o'clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.92,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait. Are we gonna film her waking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.49,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Six, then? Seven? When should we do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.74,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,If she's that set against it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:26.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,she must have a pretty serious \Nreason not to want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.59,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she just said \Nshe didn't like the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.77,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,She said that pretty bluntly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:33.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That means she probably has a \Ndeeper reason not to want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:34.97,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-chan, you're so mature!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.16,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know that yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.14,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But asking about that should \Nprobably be our first task.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.02,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,A reason, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:46.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.27,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.71,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:55.75,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:56.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Self-loathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:02.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking, \Nyou're probably right, Hinata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:07.75,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the day, I've mainly \Nbeen prioritizing my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.88,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been thinking about anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.38,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}just{\i0} realizing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.39,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:17.38,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,As they say, it's a thin line between \Nself-assertion and selfishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:18.90,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Who says that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.97,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.61,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Working today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:34.67,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.72,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Want to grab a bite, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:40.86,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Antarctica, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.19,Main,megu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you work that all out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.00,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Well... We're not sure yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.38,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:53.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:57.09,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Room 305.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.93,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do? T-T-Tail her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.30,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What good would that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,A coincidence. \NJust pretend it's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Were you staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:08.31,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.31,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.81,sign_9098_126_New_Dosanko_Prom,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b1}Math I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.81,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:17.50,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I need to catch up \Non the classes I miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:21.60,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,This place has free refills, \Nand it's open late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:23.62,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,You're so responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:25.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Antarctica, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:27.87,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I haven't made any more progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:31.24,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, we know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:34.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,There's something else we wanted to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.13,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.59,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.01,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it strange that I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.11,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, c'mon! Antarctica has penguins!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:45.26,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Icebergs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:47.74,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,And you can see the aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:50.31,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,My mother got to you, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:53.23,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Does she want you to convince me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:11:59.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:11:59.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Spineless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:06.37,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,But I still want to know the \Nreason you don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.91,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.16,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay if you don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.93,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt you would understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:26.24,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:28.19,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Not just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.19,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.05,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:36.94,sign_18052_267_Shiraishi_Yuzu_c,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi Yuzu-chan\N{\c&HBFB1E1&}Congratulations on\Nyour TV appearance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.94,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a child actress \Nsince I was four years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:41.84,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,But because I was so busy, I hardly \Nhad any time to play with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:46.34,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Then it kept happening and happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:53.79,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had a fight with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.83,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's the only one I fight with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.21,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,So once I got into high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:02.80,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I had to make \Nfriends, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.54,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I'd go to clubs, get a part-time job,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.68,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,buy sweets with my friends after class,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.97,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,do karaoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.48,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.62,Flashback,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:19.06,Flashback,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Let's go hang out some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.55,Flashback,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.57,Flashback,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.75,Flashback,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Also, can we get a picture together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:26.22,Flashback,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan's a celebrity, \Nso people want to see pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.00,Flashback,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Take one with me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.63,Flashback,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.20,Flashback,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:38.79,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,First impressions are important, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I need to start working hard \Nto form them right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:47.91,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Proper relationships and groups...\NYou're basically establishing who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.78,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.07,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to hug you suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.02,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.79,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:14:00.39,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I always hate new school terms and stuff, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:02.11,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:02.94,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:03.73,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.82,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're all best friends, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Best friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.08,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even known each other a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:19.83,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We've never even hung out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:24.05,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,We're just all trying \Nto go to the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:26.24,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,For now, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:28.91,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:29.94,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:31.05,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you out so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.56,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I hope your mother understands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:44.71,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. I feel a little better, \Nhaving gotten to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.52,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:47.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:14:57.45,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,So... where does that actually leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.46,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:02.08,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten? \NWe came here to convince her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.30,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:07.97,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But if Yuzuki-chan refuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.34,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan can go in her place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:13.42,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,If we convince her, we can go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.01,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:18.09,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but if Yuzuki-chan refuses, \NShirase-chan can go in her place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.15,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.35,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.47,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If she refuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,they'll get some other \Nentertainer to go in her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:27.69,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:30.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Convincing her was our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.43,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think this is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.42,more phone,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12}Aina: {\fs14}Can't do that either?\N{\fs12}Yuri-chan: {\fs14}How about next Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.42,sign_22698_331_Sorry____I_don_t,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I don't know just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.42,sign_22698_332_Sorry__Maybe_nex,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:54.50,Italics,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time anyone's done that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.63,Italics,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Having friends... Is that what it feels like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.93,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:38.76,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? They'll yell at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.48,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.93,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, the wind is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:46.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.48,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.06,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:43.37,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:04.39,sign_25922_344_Today_Aina_has_l,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Today\N\N07:03\NAina has left the group.\N\N07:04\NYuri-chan has left the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:32.96,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.71,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.82,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was too early! \NShe's still in her pajamas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.68,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,It was Shirase-chan who said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.67,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What was I supposed to do? \NWe're going all the way to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:44.60,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:48.96,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We heard you had a job in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:51.37,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured we could go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:53.28,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to jump on you like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.66,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because she didn't\Nask for your contact info.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:56.64,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:58.07,Main,sira,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.94,0:18:59.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:01.33,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Then, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:03.63,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to the Tokyo... Polar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.97,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:33.58,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:37.25,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who said \Nwe should go together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:10.06,Flashback,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I'll go if I can \Ngo with the three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.10,Flashback,hina,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't go without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:18.61,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Yuzuki-chan! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:20.77,Main,yuz,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:28.09,Main,shi,0000,0000,0000,,P-Penguins!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.05,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they nice and fluffy looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.26,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.25,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.99,0:20:38.09,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.34,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we can go inside this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:41.75,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.05,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty cramped in here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:50.93,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they use newer models of \Nsnowcats nowadays, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.16,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead, and keep 'er steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:55.94,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.45,0:20:59.19,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,This bunk bed only has a top bunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.16,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,It says they keep the rooms \Nover twenty degrees Celsius!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.20,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:05.86,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Because it'll be negative \Nten degrees outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I bet my nose would be running...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.58,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Come a little closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.61,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the real one is a lot more beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.40,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've heard it's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:32.27,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,My mother said it brought her to tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:36.41,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't get to see \Nthe aurora, though, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.19,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.67,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Then if we really do get to see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:46.78,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,we might be the only high school students \Nin the world to see the aurora from Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.41,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:50.53,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:58.97,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I could just die right now!
